Shannon Bream, host of FOX News @ Night on the FOX News Channel returns with new &quot;Livin&#39; The Bream&quot; podcast. This week, Shannon speaks with Lara Trump about the upcoming midterm elections, how women will vote after the confirmation of Brett Kavanaugh, life on the campaign trail, how the media continues to go after her father-in-law and what President Trump told the family prior to saying he was going to run for president, her passion for helping animals with &#39;Pets for Vets&#39;, how she nurtures her relationship with husband Eric in the spotlight all the time and her faith and how it played a role during this entire process.

